{"tid":339923,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人另一半成日失蹤？","createTime":"2017-07-29T12:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T14:42:21.000Z","uid":17168,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a372b66662377fad00620678929b52c1cf43f40f","tid":339923,"uid":17168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"拍左拖半年 平時一星期見一至三次<br />\n因為佢唔鍾意人睇佢手機 所以我都尊重佢 冇睇過<br />\n佢要乜我都盡量俾佢 乜都就晒佢 體諒佢<br />\n<br />\n最近佢對我好冷淡 <br />\n前幾日話想多d時間做自己野 話想同我做返朋友 要我等佢一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後呢幾日都係咁失蹤 一唔見人就唔見幾個鐘/成晚<br />\n<br />\n我問過我d朋友 全部都唔明白<br />\n男既就話 邊有男人會無啦啦唔要自己女朋友<br />\n女既就話 佢對你冷淡又成日失蹤 一定係有第個<br />\n<br />\n我好迷惘好唔明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問佢係咪唔愛我唔要我了 佢又話唔係<br />\n究竟姐係點？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評：繼續等佢 信佢 體諒佢 做佢朋友<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評：肯定變左心 bl左佢 搵過第二個啦！！"},{"pid":"439e1940d2f7c616bba3a1e7dd93acf0f85c4a0c","tid":339923,"uid":20882,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:54:24.000Z","msg":"仲叫你等一年 食撚屎啦佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分手就分得乾脆啲"},{"pid":"8c1c29cd16b5e0e48d0cc7eeead7792b89c8560c","tid":339923,"uid":6136,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭雞</span></span>"},{"pid":"fc45bc42286a9e338c3296352e11692aecf26ca9","tid":339923,"uid":64949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:55:07.000Z","msg":"臭雞明顯係想dum你時間，到你唔再想等佢既時候可以走圍同人講係你飛佢，佢自己先係受害者"},{"pid":"ac50ebec38b84d7f91e4e8b3caa61efec28da0a3","tid":339923,"uid":17168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲叫你等一年 食撚屎啦佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分手就分得乾脆啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我都好嬲 點解要咁自私&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"eaf3872b6fac58097cda4a3c764a42fa8bd920d5","tid":339923,"uid":17168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:55:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>臭雞明顯係想dum你時間，到你唔再想等佢既時候可以走圍同人講係你飛佢，佢自己先係受害者</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36191c27c56f04509fb11070df282899659b7806","tid":339923,"uid":64949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:56:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">條仆街</span>明顯係想dum你時間，到你唔再想等佢既時候可以走圍同人講係你飛佢，佢自己先係受害者</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36fc3ad7d696f2b72c8e540f5956fb243c79a202","tid":339923,"uid":17168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">條仆街</span>明顯係想dum你時間，到你唔再想等佢既時候可以走圍同人講係你飛佢，佢自己先係受害者</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實佢係咪想收我做兵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a0193421477adc7188e53b642b09d9008e55a2","tid":339923,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:02:36.000Z","msg":"留名等睇有人話另一半失蹤咗二十年企圖搞笑"},{"pid":"f40ea1f913fe4a6a3871775d5785317a6992d997","tid":339923,"uid":76105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"話想同我做返朋友<br />\n<br />\n佢都講到咁。你仲唔明？定呃自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺明試左半年，覺得你唔係佢杯茶，仲唔閃人咩。"},{"pid":"59a7b25ad831c82a88e228ab3554f6aaa5167001","tid":339923,"uid":17168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29